title: DarkX - August Ames [720p]
description:
Rico Strong is a hitman who works for Kane. He's been sent to take care of his bosses wife and August Ames is none-to-pleased to be a kept woman. She has needs and Rico understands them implicitly; their need for secrecy and discretion only intensifies their desire. Rico takes care of August, but not in the way that his boss had in mind.
